reviewText: A dream come true.  If your are an Amitabh fan, you will be in heaven.  Excellent quality, although they only display the movie title at the beginning of the clip, so it can be a bit hard to identify the movie.  If you have house guests who have stayed too long and aren't Bollywood fans,  you can get rid of them fast by putting this on.
Very good songs of my favorite Amitabh Bachchan.
